Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reportPowerSwitch(25.10)                              reportPowerSwitch(25.10)

Name
       reportPowerSwitch  -  Reports each power switch instance, the location,
       and pin/net connections

Syntax
       reportPowerSwitch

       [-help]

       -outFile <file_name>

       Reports each power switch instance, the location, and  pin/net  connec-
       tions. The report format is as follows:

       #InstName (x,y)

       #  (pin1): net1

       #  (pin2): net2

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for each reportPowerSwitch parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and  all  its  parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man reportPowerSwitch.

       -outFile <file_name>
              Specifies  the  name of the report file where the information is
              written. This is a required parameter.

Related Information
              * deletePowerSwitch

              * exportPowerSwitch

              * importPowerSwitch

              * movePowerSwitch

              * rechainPowerSwitch

              * replacePowerSwitch

              * verifyPowerSwitch

              * Low Power Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

